nket, you cannot have it」（如果他们不会说毛毯的英文， 那他们就不配毛毯）、「Carpet is on the floor」 （地毯是在地上）… 「应该是前排旅客努力使用自己会的英文单词想要向这些‘只会英文的’乘务员拿毛毯，结果反被取笑。」该网友称。位于该网友前排的乘客在尝试用英文询问空乘如何填写入境卡时，同样得到了无比不耐烦的回答。空乘人员歧视非英语旅客？国泰航空：将严肃调查处理 _ 直击现场 _ 澎湃新闻 -The Paper"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-0e6525acf48d69e4d73fc2044d7fc460_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "635 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/602475768"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IocyW16GIiIYXEAMaCDk2MTY0MDk0IIumrqMGMBY4jwNAA3IJNjAyNDc1NzY4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "4_1684818449.982876", "card_id": "Q_599330090", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 306}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "男友凌晨开了 3 个小时的车，就为了给我送吃的东西，不知道该不该生气？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "他买了好多不能过夜的食物给我，突然半夜给我打电话说他在送东西过来的路上。 我跟爸妈一起住的，大半夜 2 点钟让我出去拿东西，我真不知道该不该生气？ #男朋友#"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-ae395ee70cf16ae0841fbcf8966b2cb9_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "323 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/599330090"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IocyW16GIiIYXEAMaCDk1NDY1MDk4INrs1KIGMBk4gQNABHIJNTk5MzMwMDkweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "5_1684818449.983583", "card_id": "Q_602330239", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 131}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "华春莹发中国 - 中亚峰会和 G7 峰会对比图，「一个加强团结合作，一个煽动分裂对抗」，两峰会有哪些不同？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "（观察者网讯）过去的一周，东西方两场关键峰会分别在中国和日本召开，其本质却形成对比。 \t5 月 18 日至 19 日，首届中国 - 中亚峰会在西安举行，彰显出互利共赢的国际合作典范。「你方唱罢我登场」，七国集团（G7）5 月 19 日至 21 日在日本广岛召开领导人会议，却继续煽动集团对抗，渲染别国威胁，滥施霸凌行径。 \t 北京时间 20 日晚，中国外交部部长助理、发言人华春莹在社交媒体推特上发出两场峰会的对比图。左边中国 - 中亚峰会聚焦「共建未来，加强团结合作和促进发展」，配图是会议前夕游人如织、共襄峰会盛举的西安大唐不夜城。右边 G7 广岛峰会则「寻求霸权，煽动分裂对抗和压制发展」，配图是峰会首日高举手幅、抗议峰会召开的日本游行民众。 华春莹发中国 - 中亚峰会和 G7 峰会对比图：一个加强团结合作，一个煽动分裂对抗"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-a1759f8d17bc77edc93df906f01170c6_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "240 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/602330239"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IocyW16GIiIYXEAMaCDk2MTMxNjg2IPi1q6MGMAg4yAFABXIJNjAyMzMwMjM5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "6_1684818449.9846113", "card_id": "Q_601665170", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 30}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "《漫长的季节》中，大爷为什么让沈墨学钢琴？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "大爷家是普通家庭，为什么额外花费给沈墨学钢琴？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-63c0f10ce0fd31c061f8c785ec79c996_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "145 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/601665170"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4IocyW16GIiIYXEAMaCDk1OTgzODI5IL3zlqMGMAA4LUAGcgk2MDE2NjUxNzB4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "7_1684818449.9851933", "card_id": "Q_602229772", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 478}, "t